    "body": "In my opinion, this should force a graceful shutdown of the application. If the port to bind is already in use, then their will be no way to communicate with peers.\r\n\r\nTo reproduce the problem, run two beacon-chain nodes with the `--p2p-port` flag set to the same value. You would expect one to fail entirely, but it is silently failing to bind to the port. ",
